@tronglass was in town recently and we got to get a sick one in! We put Matt’s bubbler style mouthpiece on a MoonLander body and then he went in with his sculpting on it. Big biomechanical vibes on this one, and the function is wild! I recently made a few tweaks to the sizing of the landers and I love the change in function. It’s such a fun piece to pull on, currently available, but I can’t imagine for too long. DM to inquire, thanks for looking

 A Parlay Event
9/2

Super stoked to present my latest grip of work at @parlayphl 2023. 
The homies @ogrefarms will be doing a pop-up and I’ve got a special giveaway planned! Be there when doors open for the best chance to win it! 
Catch us @frontstgallery on day 2, 9/2 at 4pm-7pm. 

Can’t wait to kick it with everyone and many thanks to @kindaglass @frontstgallery and the rest of the parlay crew for having me out there. It’s gonna be a blast!

Parlay 2023 was a blast! Thank you to everyone that came out to my show during this year’s Parlay. Had a great time chopping it up with the homies and meeting some new ones.

Thank you @kindaglass @frontstgallery for giving me the opportunity to display my work for the masses and thanks to everyone else in the @parlayphl crew that helped out.

Shoutout to @ogrefarms for joining me and killing it with their pop up. 

Can’t wait to see what’s in store for next year.
